        {
          "type": "narration",
          "role": "narrator",
          "text": {
            "en": "Emperor Ashoka stands over silent Kalinga, victory ash in his mouth, as the dead haunt his heart. From that pain, he turns to dhamma, vowing a new rule of care, not swords.",
